## PARAGRAPH\_VARIANTS variable

Read-only array that contains all paragraph style variants

**Signature:**

```typescript
PARAGRAPH_VARIANTS: readonly ["normal", "h1", "h2", "h3", "h4", "h5", "h6", "title", "subtitle", "preamble", "code"]
```
